dcterms:creator: S. Fujimoto
H. van Hoof
D. Meger
dcterms:description: The Near-Expert Dataset consists of experience collected from a TD3 agent trained for 1M steps, followed by rolling out the policy with Gaussian noise to collect 4M experience on each task.
dcterms:title: Near-Expert Dataset

dcterms:creator: D. Yarats
R. Fergus
A. Lazaric
L. Pinto
dcterms:description: The Mixed Dataset consists of diverse data collected from various agents, including 2K near-expert trajectories for each task and 10M exploratory trajectories using intrinsic reward from Proto-RL.
dcterms:title: Mixed Dataset

dcterms:creator: D. Yarats
R. Fergus
A. Lazaric
L. Pinto
dcterms:description: The Mixed-v2 Dataset is an updated version of the Mixed Dataset, containing unsupervised, semi-supervised, and supervised data collected from various agents.
dcterms:title: Mixed-v2 Dataset
